title: NYCC 2018: First Look At Geoff Johns's Shazam Series From DC Comics
body:
NYCC 2018: First Look At Geoff Johns’s Shazam Series From DC Comics

At Geoff Johns Spotlight Panel this past weekend at NYCC, amongst other things he spoke about, he updated fans on Shazam, a series that will debut on November 21st with art by Dale Eaglesham, who I cannot rate highly enoughand the perfect fit for this title. Well, here’s some naked black and white pages that I’m calling a preview, even without the colour or lettering. It’s gorgeous work and…
